♪ dreadful sorry, Clementine

1317
01:03:26,868 --> 01:03:29,968
♪ Ruby lips above the water

1318
01:03:30,067 --> 01:03:33,901
♪ blowing bubbles
soft and fine ♪

1319
01:03:33,968 --> 01:03:36,567
♪ well, as for me,
I was no swimmer ♪

1320
