1721
01:23:26,534 --> 01:23:29,234
Hold on
to that peg there.

1722
01:23:29,300 --> 01:23:30,534
You o.K., Michael?

1723
01:23:30,601 --> 01:23:33,234
Chip, just keep
looking up here.

1724
01:23:33,300 --> 01:23:34,767
I got you, man.

1725
01:23:34,834 --> 01:23:36,534
