1731
01:23:46,400 --> 01:23:48,234
Right here, buddy.

1732
01:23:48,300 --> 01:23:50,267
O.k.!

1733
01:23:50,334 --> 01:23:51,968
Got him?

1734
01:23:52,067 --> 01:23:54,267
Yeah, I got him.

1735
01:23:54,334 --> 01:23:56,367
We're almost
out of here.

1736
01:23:56,434 --> 01:23:59,534
