a camping trip.

1756
01:24:43,968 --> 01:24:47,634
I got you.

1757
01:24:47,701 --> 01:24:48,901
Come on, dad.

1758
01:24:55,300 --> 01:24:56,934
Dad!

1759
01:25:11,133 --> 01:25:12,434
