not exactly,

1846
01:29:15,434 --> 01:29:18,334
but...i really want
to thank you

1847
01:29:18,400 --> 01:29:20,067
for making me go.

1848
01:29:20,100 --> 01:29:23,868
It was one
of the best things
you've done

1849
01:29:23,934 --> 01:29:26,367
for Michael
and for me.

1850
01:29:26,434 --> 01:29:28,334
Thank you.

1851
01:29:29,634 --> 01:29:31,567
Well, you're welcome.

1852
01:29:31,634 --> 01:29:34,400
I'm proud of you.

1853
01:29:34,467 --> 01:29:36,267
Thanks.

1854
01:29:36,334 --> 01:29:38,067
This was just
the beginning.

1855
01:29:38,133 --> 01:29:41,567
Michael and I will
spend more guy time
together.

1856
01:29:41,634 --> 01:29:43,701
We'll go
to baseball games

1857
01:29:43,767 --> 01:29:45,400
and basketball
games.

1858
01:29:45,467 --> 01:29:47,200
Great.
Michael will love that.

1859
01:29:47,267 --> 01:29:51,200
Next weekend,
we start our scuba
diving lessons.

1860
01:29:52,601 --> 01:29:54,267
Let's check
on our kid.

1861
01:29:54,334 --> 01:29:56,767
Sc-scuba diving?

1862
01:29:56,834 --> 01:29:59,767
I'm glad
you guys bonded
and everything,

1863
01:29:59,834 --> 01:30:03,567
but when I said
you should do
guy things,

1864
01:30:03,634 --> 01:30:06,767
I meant like
playing catch
in the driveway.

1865
01:30:06,834 --> 01:30:09,133
Aw...

1866
01:30:31,334 --> 01:30:32,934
Good night, pal.

1867
01:30:40,634 --> 01:30:44,033
So what do you think
of white-water rafting?

1868
01:30:44,100 --> 01:30:46,100
This is what
you always do--

1869
01:30:46,167 --> 01:30:47,467
you get
a good idea

1870
01:30:47,534 --> 01:30:49,634
and go overboard
with it.

1871
01:30:49,701 --> 01:30:52,300
It's a nice way to relax
after bungee jumping.

1872
01:30:52,367 --> 01:30:54,100
Let's talk
about this.

